cochaired the president�s task force to improve health care delivery for our nation�s veterans and in  served as a commissioner on the president�s commission on care for america�s returning wounded warriors doleshalala commission dr wilensky testifies frequently before congressional committees serves as an advisor to members of congress and other elected officials speaks nationally and internationally before professional business and consumer groups she received a bachelor�s degree in psychology and a phd in economics at the university of michigan and has received several honorary degrees gail wilensky as heard on wtop  fm read more and listen meet dr gail wilensky video clips each video is approximately  minutes best viewed in ie  or less meet dr gail wilensky video gail wilensky the world health care congress  interview studio cspan august    gail wilensky th anniversary of medicare is it working march   bloomberg news comments on �america�s healthcare overhall bill� march   pbs newshour with jeffrey brown cbo estimates for health care reform january   bloomberg news what the budget numbers mean november   pbs newshour with judy woodruff counting the cost of health care reform september   newshour wjim lehrer the future of medicare advantage august   newshour wjim lehrer what healthcare reform might mean for senior citizens june   bloomberg news challenges ahead for health care reform june   bloomberg news the  trillion question health care reform december   washington journal future of military health care december   abc world news with charles gibson dr tim johnson  critical condition   windows media player required for viewing download or update your windows media player here the official web site for gail wilensky phd copyright  gail wilensky phd        for additional information please contact gloria burrell gburrellprojecthopeorg or call   gail wilensky phd gail r wilensky exclusive editions last updated february  perspective new england journal of medicine 